                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The MONTE CARLO simulation"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The major difficulty in measuring the",
                "p+d-p+d+eta reaction is the huge background coming fro",
                "other pd-x channels. The eta-peak is clear seen in the",
                "proton-deuteron missing mass distribution at all",
                "energies."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Such uncertainties in the rate of nuclear interactions",
                "introduce systematic errors in the final cross sections",
                "varying from 10% at 927-MeV to 17% at 1096-MeV,to these",
                "must be added the overall normalization error of 20%",
                "quoted for the p+d-He-3+Eta reaction."
              ]
            }
          ],
